Text: RE PA and ETA topicspst Rick just informed me that he will be unable to participate in this conference call He still wants the call to take place as scheduled Thanks Debra Original Message From Kimmel Debra FI Sent Friday January PM To Flood Scott L GCO Stuckey Richard A FI Casaudoumecq John FI Kitchen Louise Costa Randall GCO Subject PA and ETA topics A conference call has been scheduled for Monday January th for am to discuss the PA and ETA topics with Enron Below is the information for the conference call Toll Free Number Passcode ETA Leader Richard Stuckey Confirm Any questions contact Debra Kimmel at Thanks Debra
